{"tid":2077200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無敵神驅：話我轉軚支持泛民者(Barry Ma)，都是卑劣鼠輩！","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T04:51:50.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2a281cfa131b8d7bdda80339805e03412dceaf04","tid":2077200,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0CtjN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0CtjN9.png&h=1b2b43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來尋晚啤梨批評無敵神驅轉軚，搞到神驅反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z6SmnhTx0uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz6SmnhTx0uk&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=a33d9ecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z6SmnhTx0uk</a><br />\n<br />\n神驅嗰啲唔係叫做支持泛民。神驅個D叫尊重民意。<br />\n<br />\n而家個個都求初選下，咪大大方方選一次囉<br />\n<br />\n如果到最後D人繼續含淚投票，你哋都要尊重，呢個先係民主。<br />\n<br />\n到時就唔係再繼續屌泛民就可以解決到嘅問題，<br />\n<br />\n係連你哋自己都要作出反省，反省下點解啲人唔投你哋票，而唔係繼續屌票。<br />\n<br />\n你可以話神驅天真地相信初選係真初選，但佢唔係轉軚。"},{"pid":"99b98832faedcfc096158cb7ce69573722d940d2","tid":2077200,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15d962ff6a3f461291420466a53bc429b60eb79","tid":2077200,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"泛民同大陸人有乜分別<br />\n口說不 身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44984fcfe8f40d7408a04ec86635be298a657cd7","tid":2077200,"uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"無敵神驅：再狂屌泛民已經無意思，適當時候係需要向民意妥協！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84de4e554434c574e513c343cba0a356c8f828